(b) Find the turns ratio V1/V2 and confirm it equals N1/N2
(c) A 10Ω load on the secondary draws current I2. Find I2.
(d) Primary current I1 from power balance: V1×I1 = V2×I2. Find I1.
(e) What would N2 need to be to produce 12V on the secondary?
